quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Kandi nyuma ye ntitwigeze twoherereza abantu be ingabo ziturutse mu kirere (zo kubarimbura), ndetse nta n’ubwo byari ngombwa ko tuzohereza"
  36,29,Ukurimburwa kwabo kwabaye (gukubitwa n’) urusaku rumwe gusa; nuko barazima (barapfa)
  36,30,Mbega akababaro ku bagaragu! Nta ntumwa yabageragaho ngo babure kuyinnyega
  36,31,Ese ntibabona ibisekuru tworetse mbere yabo uko bingana? (Ntibabona) ko mu by’ukuri batagaruka (ngo bongere kubana na bo)
  36,32,"Kandi rwose, bose bazazanwa imbere yacu"
  36,33,"Kandi ikimenyetso kuri bo ni ubutaka bwapfuye (bwakakaye) dusubiza ubuzima, maze tukabukuramo imyaka bafungura"
  36,34,"Ndetse twanabushyizeho ubusitani bw’imitende n’imizabibu, tunavuburamo amasoko"
  36,35,Kugira ngo bafungure ku mbuto zayo ndetse n’ibyakozwe n’amaboko yabo. Ese ntibashobora gushimira
  36,36,"Ubutagatifu ni ubw’uwaremye ibitsina byombi (ikigabo n’ikigore); byaba mu bimera mu butaka byose, muri bo ubwabo (abantu) ndetse no mu byo batazi"
  36,37,Kandi n’ikimenyetso kuri bo ni ijoro; turikuraho (umucyo w’) amanywa maze bakaba mu mwijima
  36,38,"Kandi izuba rigana mu mwanya ryashyiriweho (ni ikimenyetso kuri bo). Uko ni ukugena k’Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  36,39,"Ndetse n’ukwezi (ni ikimenyetso kuri bo). Twagushyiriyeho ibyiciro kunyuramo, kugeza ubwo kongeye kuba nk’ishami ry’umutende rishaje"
  36,40,Izuba ntirishobora guhurirana n’ukwezi cyangwa ngo ijoro rize mu mwanya w’amanywa. Kandi byose byogoga mu myanya yabyo
  36,41,N’ikindi kimenyetso kuri bo ni uko twatwaye urubyaro rwabo mu bwato (bwa Nuhu) bwikoreye (n’ibindi)
  36,42,Twanabaremeye ibindi bisa na bwo bagenderaho
  36,43,"Kandi iyo tubishatse turabarohamisha, maze ntibabone ubatabara cyangwa ngo barokorwe"
  36,44,"Uretse ku bw’impuhwe ziduturutseho, n’ibyishimo by’igihe gito"
  36,45,"N’iyo babwiwe bati “Nimugandukire ibiri imbere yanyu (ibihano byo ku isi) n’ibiri inyuma yanyu (ibihano byo ku mperuka), kugira ngo mugirirwe impuhwe (ntibumva).”"
  36,46,Kandi nta kimenyetso na kimwe mu bimenyetso bya Nyagasani wabo cyabageragaho ngo babure kugitera umugongo
  36,47,"N’iyo babwiwe bati “Nimutange mu byo Allah yabahaye, abahakanyi babwira abemeramana bati “Ese muragira ngo dufungurire uwo Allah yari gufungurira iyo aza kubishaka? Mwe nta handi muri hatari mu buyobe bugaragara.”"
  36,48,"Baranavuga bati “Ese iryo sezerano (izuka) rizaba ryari, niba koko muri abanyakuri?”"
  36,49,Nta kindi bategereje usibye urusaku rumwe (rw’impanda ya mbere) ruzabakubita bahugiye mu mpaka
  36,50,Nuko ntibashobore kugira umurage basiga habe no gusubira mu miryango yabo
  36,51,"Nuko impanda ivuzwe (bwa kabiri), maze bahite basohoka mu mva (zabo) bagana kwa Nyagasani wabo bihuta"
  36,52,"Bavuga bati “Mbega ishyano tubonye! Ni nde utuzuye akadukura mu buryamo bwacu?” (Bazabwirwa bati) “Ibi ni byo Nyirimpuhwe yasezeranyije, kandi intumwa zavuze ukuri.”"
  36,53,"(Izurwa ryabo) rizaterwa n’urusaku rumwe (rw’impanda), nuko ubwo bahite bazanwa imbere yacu"
  36,54,"(Babwirwe bati) “Uyu munsi nta muntu n’umwe uri bugire icyo ahuguzwa, kandi nta kindi muri buhemberwe usibye ibyo mwakoraga.”"
  36,55,Mu by’ukuri abantu bo mu ijuru kuri uwo munsi bazaba bahugijwe n’umunezero
  36,56,"Bo n’abagore babo bazaba bari mu gicucu, bicaye begamye mu bitanda by’imisego myiza"
  36,57,Bazarihabwamo imbuto (z’ubwoko bwose) ndetse banabonemo ibyo bashaka byose
  36,58,"(Bazabwirwa bati) “Salamu (mugire amahoro)!” Izaba ari imvugo iturutse kwa Nyagasani, Nyirimbabazi"
  36,59,Inkozi z’ibibi (zizabwirwa ziti) “Uyu munsi nimwigireyo mwa nkozi z’ibibi mwe (nimwitandukanye n’abemeramana).”